name: The Rat Trap by Cheese Labs

metadata.name: RAT TRAP #1
metadata.description:
The Rat Trap is a collection of 5555 characters, in which humans are represented by rats to illustrate the concept of the rat race.

 Each NFT entitles the holder to exclusive benefits and access to solutions developed by the Cheese Lab, The Rat Trap's solution development lab.

 The Rat Trap aims to respond to the challenges and changing issues that the web3 world brings, through innovative and user friendly solutions that will change the daily life of their holders, and ease the onboarding of newcomers into web3.

 Visit our [website](https://www.therattrap.io/) for more details.
